org.mixare.lib.render

Class Matrix

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mixare.lib.render.Matrix

  • public class Matrix
extends java.lang.Object
    The Matrix class represents a 3x3 matrix which can store decimal numbers. Several modification can be done with a stored matrix. (for example inverting or adding another matrix)
